Package: hmrc
Title: Download and Tidy HMRC Statistical Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Charles", "Coverdale", , "charlescoverdale@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to download, parse, and tidy statistical
    data published by HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) on GOV.UK, including
    tax receipts, National Insurance contributions, and property
    transactions. File URLs are resolved at runtime via the GOV.UK
    Content API <https://www.gov.uk/api/content>, ensuring data is always
    current. Files are cached locally between sessions.
